Updating a working copy (or selectively, certain files or directories)
-----------------------------------------

1. Right click on a file/directory
   -------------------------------
   The directory/file must be a part of a SVN working copy which was
   previously checked out.

   Not yet implemented.

2. Right click on multiple items
   -----------------------------
   All the slected items need to be part of a working copy.
   In the update dialog is possible to deselect a few of them.

   Not yet implemented.

3. Right click on background
   -------------------------
   The current directory needs to be part of a working copy.
   An update operation will be ran on the current directory.

   Not yet implemented.
